  "text": "The effectiveness of SVM depends on the selection of objective function parameter C, kernel parameter and non-sensitivity coefficient ε. There is currently no widely accepted best way to optimize SVM parameters. Grid search (GS) with exponentially growing sequences of combination {C, g} is often applied [CITATION_1] . Grid search is easy to implement but has low computing efficiency. Moreover, optimal result of grid search can only generate from existing grid combinations, while unknown possible better parameters can not be explored and discovered.",
